latestIgtvVideos.title: Fluffy Brows
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Clear Brow Set (great to comb hairs up and keep them in place)
Tip: apply later allow to dry reapply for them to stay in place all day and add texture
Eyeshadow: Sandstone, Mystery, Coquette, Brun 
Use brush 242 for quick application or 263 for more detail
Eyesbrows Styler: great to fill in gaps add texture and definition
Tip: you can start w priming brow bone w prep prime 24 hr eyebase all over brows then draw on hairs. 
Eyebrows Big boost Fibre gel- great for adding texture, changing or coating brow hairs w color and quick step to add volume to brows. 
Shape Shade Brow tint shade Taupe: micro blading effect, water color looking pen you cant mess up. Draw on hairs for most natural finish.

💄💋🫦 
Easiest way to bump up look: Add a Lipstick!
Happy Mothers day Weekend! #redlips #lipstick #quickglam

How to SPF skin 

Start skin prep with light moisturizer.
Mix a few drops of your SPF with 1-2 drops of your foundation/Concealer. This will give you high protection with a more blended natural finish. Also bronzer at end is optional or I recommend if you still want to add more warmth to skin.
